=========================================================================
  claude-cli-cloud-run — pre-built Claude Code dev environment
=========================================================================
  Tools:     claude, uv, cargo, rustc, clippy, rustfmt, git, gh, vim,
             tmux, ripgrep, jq, tini, build-essential, openssh

  Workdir:   ~/workspaces  (bind-mounted; clone repos here)

  Start claude:
      claude --dangerously-skip-permissions

  Python, use uv for venv and package management:
      uv venv .venv
      uv add <package>  # adds to pyproject.toml and installs
      uv sync           # install from pyproject.toml

  GitHub auth (one of):
      If you did not set GH_TOKEN in .env or values.yaml:
      gh auth login                  # interactive
      export GH_TOKEN=ghp_...        # or set GH_TOKEN in .env / Secret

  Tmux auto-start (Helm):
      Set claude.autoStartTmux.enabled=true in values.yaml
      Attach: tmux attach -t claude

  Persisted via mounts:
      ~/.claude{,.json}
      ~/.ssh
      ~/.config/gh
      ~/workspaces

  Tokens (auto-exported to shells from ENV or Secret; set in .env or Helm values):
      GH_TOKEN, HF_TOKEN
=========================================================================
